
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 06 of Thoracic MRT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Upper abdomen, liver/gall bladder' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Focal liver lesion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Diffuse liver lesion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cholelithiasis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Wall thickening of the gallbladder' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Focal liver lesion' checkbox
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu is enabled
And '> 1 lesion of the same entity' checkbox is enabled

When I select any diagnosis from 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspicion of' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Diffuse liver lesion' checkbox
Then 'Hepatic steatosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Hepatitis cirrhosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Hemosiderosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Not further specified' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Hepatitis cirrhosis' radio button
Then 'Suspicion of' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Hemosiderosis' radio button
Then 'Suspicion of' checkbox is enabled
